com.cyber2.api.lib.client.reader

Class AbstractReaderAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyber2.api.lib.client.AbstractClientAdapter
      • com.cyber2.api.lib.client.reader.AbstractReaderAdapter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractBaseReaderAdapter, OwnerReaderAdapter

    public abstract class AbstractReaderAdapter
extends AbstractClientAdapter

    Base client class used by com.cyber2.api.lib.client.reader and com.cyber2.api.lib.client.writer. Conceptually works as an adapter with a Connection and a RequestExecutor.

    Implementing classes should abstract away low level API calls to the RequestExecutor and return high-level com.cyber2.api.lib.entities style classes.
